    VECTORS    (X)  : origin=0x00000000 length=0x00000100 fill=0xFFFFFFFF
    VECTORSNEW (X)  : origin=0x00000100 length=0x00000020 fill=0xFFFFFFFF
    FLASH0     (RX) : origin=0x00000120 length=0x001FFEE0 vfill=0xFFFFFFFF
